    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The activity of creating photographs for advertising, communication, display, instruction, or other industrial uses. Typically commercial photography is undertaken for catalogs, brochures, manuals, press releases, and advertisements.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
